if you don't believe me.

307
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,140
Excuse me.

308
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:07,980
I have to take this call.

309
00:18:10,060 --> 00:18:10,940
Hello, Mr. Wu.

310
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:13,140
How could you bring an elderly person

311
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:14,220
