334
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:06,140
Mr. Wu,

335
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:06,900
you see.

336
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:08,660
We'll go home for one day.

337
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:09,300
