345
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:21,460
Yes,

346
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:23,060
the ant kingdom.

347
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:26,660
Mr. Wu,

348
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:27,500
you see.

349
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,180
