352
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:34,620
Don't worry.

353
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:35,940
I'll send him back here tomorrow.

354
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:39,220
All right, fine.

355
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:40,860
Okay, listen.

356
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:42,300
If there's any issue,

357
00:19:42,980 --> 00:19:44,700
