358
00:19:45,420 --> 00:19:46,460
I'll give Putao a call, too.

359
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:47,260
All right.

360
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:48,060
Thank you.

361
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:52,060
Mr. Wang,

362
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,020
let's go home.

363
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:53,860
Okay.

