These dishes
were freshly made yesterday.

379
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:39,460
Xiwen said she wanted
to eat braised meat.

380
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:41,540
And she's sitting
for her grade exam tomorrow.

381
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:42,220
Why is it...

382
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:43,020
Mr. Wang,

383
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,060
calm down.

384
00:22:44,300 --> 00:22:44,780
There's no need to rush.

385
00:22:44,980 --> 00:22:45,220
Calm down?

